.IP \fIevent_mode\fP 1i
Specifies the event mode.
You can pass one of these constants:
.PN AsyncPointer , 
.PN SyncPointer , 
.PN AsyncKeyboard , 
.PN SyncKeyboard ,
.PN ReplayPointer , 
.PN ReplayKeyboard ,
.PN AsyncBoth ,
or
.PN SyncBoth .
